Quickstrike:






Quickstrike stared on for a while, eyeing Wrath as he escaped. His last 
words lingered in his optics. Better? He was better than him? He'd like to 
go one on one with the fool and find out who was really better.

He made an annoyed noise, watching as the fool-Maximal left his optics. He 
was mad. It was a good chance of a fight he had been waiting for. A fight 
against the Maximals, not against other Predacon.

Now was the time to get himself back to base. He walked over to Stingtra, 
asking as he stood in front of her, "Where's yer damage?"
